SCHEMA: materials/connection_type.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.materials.connection_type
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define canonical connection type tags for AG edges.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record connection_type
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - connection_type_id: id
    - description: string
    - extensions: map
  optional:
    - requires_part_classes: list<id>

INVARIANTS:
- Connection types are declarative tags only at MAT-3.
